<center><h1>Main Chef</h1></center>
<div class="card" id="chef_card_center">
  <img src="guy.jpg" alt="guy" style="width:100%">
  <div class="container">
    <br><center><h4><b>Guy Savoy - three michelin stars</b></h4><center>
    <p class="card_text">Guy Savoy is a world renowned Chef who through his numerous Parisian Restaurants has brought high quality French cooking to the World. His three Michelin Stars speak volumes about his skills as a chef. With his focus on only using the very best locally sourced ingredients, he is able to provide an unmatched culinary experience. Through his work at Le Brume Salée, he is seeking to bringing French cuisine to new environments. In these new surroundings, Chef Savoy, however continues to ground his work in traditional French fare, with an emphasis on Bourgogne specialties.
</p>
  </div>
