    <p class="card_text">One of the most exciting young chefs from the United States, in coming to Le Brume Salée, Tom brings an incredibly creative culinary pallet from his New York restaurants. The modern American cuisine from his New York restaurants is known for its creativity and unconventionality, all while adhering to an incredibly high qualitative standard.
      <br><br>
    </p>
